{"tid":2056812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"無左連登, 抗爭文宣可能大受打擊","createTime":"2020-06-09T03:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T05:26:43.000Z","uid":134071,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"029833ed0594faa005ce361f89cf7ff85ccb0e25","tid":2056812,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:05:55.000Z","msg":"連登對勇武抗爭行動無咩影響, 但對非暴力抗爭依然有好大影響.<br />\n<br />\n德國外長老屈黃之鋒提倡港獨, 其實藍絲已經講左幾日, 仲話德國外長的說話足以證明黃之鋒犯國安法.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp; 但黃絲無咩人理.<br />\n直至我係連登post單野, 先至有好多人係twitter狂轟德國外長. &nbsp;(唔係讚自己, 因為我自己都太後知後覺.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n根據我的觀察, 網絡有兩樣野係網絡特別傳播得快:<br />\n- 飯民做柒事 (利申: 覺得李柱銘谷, 吳文遠最近既野係抵屌.)<br />\n- 全球左膠做柒事.<br />\n<br />\n其他野, 絕對大部分真係要靠連登傳播.<br />\n國安法後, 一定封連登 (曾鈺成都話連登要收斂), 到時抗爭文宣真係唔知點算. &nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea79e046ab0f15128934c1013bcd1fc6ed1ffab","tid":2056812,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfaf39214876cc4284b90f2d86e31696a38cf54","tid":2056812,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:11:12.000Z","msg":"貼吧見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f82c93839d3015456f2a4774d491cb7dc01b8a","tid":2056812,"uid":151313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:14:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e325f5210f4c4b8580cd2847185554d1cbe70fec","tid":2056812,"uid":261627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"029833ed0594faa005ce361f89cf7ff85ccb0e25","tid":2056812,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"rep